options.graphics.fabulous.tooltip:
§r󰀆 §cFabulous!§r
 §a+§r Custom skybox.
 §a+§r Draws weather, clouds and particles behind translucent blocks and water.

§r󰀆 §eFancy§r
 §a+§r Waving leaves.
 §c-§r Custom skybox turn off.
 §c-§r Weather, clouds, and particles may not appear behind translucent blocks or water.

§r󰀆 §aFast§r
 §c-§r Waving leaves turn off.
 §c-§r Reduces the amount of visible rain and snow.
